&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/zeit/hyper&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;hyper 
















  &lt;img src=&#34;https://ng-tech.icu/assets/code.svg&#34; style=&#34;max-width: 100px;display: inline-flex;&#34;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: A terminal built on web technologies.&lt;/p&gt;
